                <expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>aio</ex></expan> Vallio <lb n="2"/>Maximiano <lb n="3"/><expan><abbr>proc</abbr><ex>uratori</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>provinciar</abbr><ex>um</ex></expan> <lb n="4"/>Macedoniae Lusi<lb break="no" n="5"/>taniae <expan><abbr>Mauretan</abbr><ex>iae</ex></expan> <lb n="6"/>Tingitanae fortis<lb break="no" n="7"/>simo duci <lb n="8"/>res <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>ublica</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Italicens</abbr><ex>ium</ex></expan> ob <lb n="9"/>merita et quot <note>sic</note> <lb n="10"/>provinciam <expan><abbr>Baetic</abbr><ex>am</ex></expan> <lb n="11"/>caesis hostibus <lb n="12"/>paci pristinae <lb n="13"/>restituerit </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> Dedicata anno <lb n="2"/>Licini Victoris et <lb n="3"/>Fabi Aeliani <expan><abbr>IIviror</abbr><ex>orum</ex></expan> <lb n="4"/><expan><abbr>pr</abbr><ex>idie</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Kal</abbr><ex>endas</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Ianuar</abbr><ex>ias</ex></expan>
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Die Datierungsangabe befindet sich auf der Nebenseite. Datierung: Nach Thomason ist der in der Inschrift erwähnte Mauereinfall wohl um 177/178 anzuseten.</p>
